## Authentication

Usage of GOV.UK Content Performance API currently requires authentication using an OAuth2 bearer token. Please [contact the team](#support) first if you are interested in using the API.

To authenticate, include an Authorization header like the following:

```
Authorization: Bearer your-token-here
```

